title: Cory Booker Presidential Campaign Press Secretary
itunes:title: Cory Booker Presidential Campaign Press Secretary
description:
Kevin spoke with Mattie Duppler, Senior Fellow at the National Taxpayers Union and former Former Coalitions Director for the House Republican Conference, and Marc Ross, founder of Caracal Global. They discussed the jobs report, immigration, the census, and President Donald Trump's comments earlier today.

Kevin also spoke with  Sabrina Singh, Booker Presidential Campaign National Press Secretary. They discussed Sen. Cory Booker's 2020 presidential campaign.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
